Waymar STCCBSE Description
This Waymar 35 gallon single compartment laminate trash container is designed to keep your dining area clean and reduce clean up when the day is done! This tray top trash container is ideal for fast food dining rooms, diners, and food courts. The self edged laminate exterior of this tray top trash container provides resistance to smudging and stains. Featuring a single compartment and a 35 gallon capacity, this laminate exterior trash container will easily blend into most waste receptacle areas seamlessly. The hinged trash lid and access floor with magnetic catch prevents waste from falling out and keeps the contents of the trash container discreet. The almond interior liner is easy to remove and will stand up to the demand of even the busiest of venues. The top black plastic tray tops wrangle your trays together and prevent them from sliding.
Trash Container Module, single, self edged laminate exterior&face frame, (1) 35 gallon rigid liner, gravity return trash swing door, access door w/ magnetic catch, almond lined interior, leveling glides, black plastic tray stops, black metal base, closed bottom. Liner included. As with all high quality restaurant furniture, this product is manufactured to meet your specific design requirements at the time you place the order. It is not in stock and typically ships in 4+ weeks. There are dozens of stain colors to choose from for the exposed wood surfaces and hundreds of colors and finishes for the laminate surfaces some of which may be at additional cost. You can also choose from optional wording on the hinged door. Contact customer service to obtain a price and availability quote for your specific needs and samples of laminates if needed to ensure a color match. This product ships direct form the manufacturer. Since all Waymar products are customized to your specifications there are no returns or refunds after we place the order with the manufacturer.
